Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.09,0:00:41.55,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多想与你倾诉　却已然难以释怀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.01,0:00:44.01,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长此积蓄
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.39,0:00:47.49,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宛如末日来临
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.06,0:00:56.10,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知该如何表达心中层层所念
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.14,0:01:00.69,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样也无法传递至伊人的心田
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.31,0:01:03.52,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,徘徊在这似近又远的距离
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.40,0:01:08.03,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空永远是一片蔚蓝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.61,0:01:12.45,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白不该就这样放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.53,0:01:15.87,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转啊转　辗转反侧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.12,0:01:19.54,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转啊转　天旋地转
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.17,0:01:23.63,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乔装彷徨的我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.63,0:01:27.13,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想投入你怀中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.22,0:01:30.59,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转啊转　辗转反侧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.84,0:01:34.18,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转啊转　天旋地转
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.72,0:01:37.73,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻轻浮起的我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.73,0:01:43.73,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天又将一个人飞上云端
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.56,0:00:04.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,School Rumble  即将开始！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.31,0:00:08.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会给你幸福的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.25,0:00:15.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不曾考虑过你的心情就说出这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.76,0:00:17.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会显得我有些厚颜无耻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.59,0:00:20.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我还是要说  跟我来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.27,0:00:28.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塚  塚本被…劫走了！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.73,0:02:03.71,tiaofu-r,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-90\pos(630,245)}不向天满表达任何心意、
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.73,0:02:03.71,tiaofu-l,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-90\pos(15,245)}就向美国出发的乌丸。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.71,0:02:08.73,tiaofu-r,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-90\pos(630,245)}恋情真的就此宣告终结吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.71,0:02:08.73,tiaofu-l,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-90\pos(15,245)}而播磨的爱慕将会如何呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.48,0:02:13.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,播磨同学  你要去哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.41,0:02:14.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样会让我很困扰的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.89,0:02:16.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说话  当心咬到舌头
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.13,0:02:18.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们正前往机场
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.60,0:02:22.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.33,0:02:24.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是去见乌丸同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.92,0:02:28.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  我不想去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.69,0:02:31.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么？你想让我和乌丸同学见面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.52,0:02:32.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么做是为了我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.74,0:02:34.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了  没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.55,0:02:36.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,播磨同学你在听吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.50,0:02:37.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下  停下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.01,0:02:40.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用再擅自帮我做这些事了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.51,0:02:41.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是怎么想的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.85,0:02:42.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了  放我下来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.20,0:02:45.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说别再多管闲事了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.89,0:03:01.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,播磨学长  又把自己的心意丢在一旁了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.58,0:03:03.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去机场了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.73,0:03:04.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.29,0:03:07.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让姐姐见乌丸学长一面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.41,0:03:11.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真被我料到了  那个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.19,0:03:14.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要这么说他  播磨学长他可是很拼命的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.25,0:03:17.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊  八云
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.46,0:03:20.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得就凭那胡子他会准备好机票吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.81,0:03:23.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙绝对把坐飞机这事当作乘电车一样简单
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.19,0:03:27.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得播磨就这么突然跑出去  钱包里还会有买票的钱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.24,0:03:31.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管再怎么逞能  到了机场还不是白费心思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.05,0:03:36.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.95,0:03:40.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问去美国的始发班机是在羽田机场  还是在成田机场
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.21,0:03:42.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国际航班的话  应该是成田吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.41,0:03:44.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.49,0:03:45.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.12,0:03:47.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绑架啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.67,0:03:48.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是我妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.89,0:03:51.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切  如此干劲十足到底是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.60,0:03:53.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到美国两万日元够了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.77,0:03:54.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放我下来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.07,0:03:55.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出这么多已经是底线了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.79,0:03:58.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说我为什么要干这事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.93,0:04:00.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前面的两人  停车
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.84,0:04:02.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把车停路边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.64,0:04:05.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切  在这紧要关头…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.46,0:04:09.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快停下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.21,0:04:17.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前面的两人  现在立刻停车
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.16,0:04:22.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.12,0:04:26.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本警察真是优秀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.33,0:04:28.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎  怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.97,0:04:30.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.43,0:04:35.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东乡雅一  参上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.66,0:04:37.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  你在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.23,0:04:39.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻下车  会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.96,0:04:43.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能急刹车的  唯有摩托与恋爱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.55,0:04:46.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.22,0:04:47.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的表情就像在说「你们为什么会在这啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.87,0:04:48.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月代头小子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.13,0:04:52.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勿需多言  英雄对于同伴的危机是很敏感的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.96,0:04:54.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然想这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.86,0:04:57.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实是晶打来了电话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.81,0:05:00.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们助你一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.56,0:05:02.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有爱理在联络航班
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.58,0:05:05.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美琴和八云在帮忙整理行装
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.48,0:05:07.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晶她们…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.78,0:05:08.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.66,0:05:09.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.61,0:05:10.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.65,0:05:15.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎现在没工夫闲聊了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.42,0:05:17.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.26,0:05:17.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后会有期
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.79,0:05:19.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  危险
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.77,0:05:21.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人与危险同在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.13,0:05:23.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.90,0:05:26.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？连爱理她们都…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.25,0:05:28.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.85,0:05:29.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塚本
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.79,0:05:32.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千万别松手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.60,0:05:44.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宫野木
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.61,0:05:45.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是往这边走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.00,0:05:46.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汽油呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.70,0:05:47.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.45,0:05:48.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢你了  弦子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.76,0:05:51.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一时粗心没注意计量表
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.73,0:05:53.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该能到达吧  拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.56,0:05:59.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我来保护她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.42,0:06:04.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是逊毙了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.71,0:06:07.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是被以前的自己看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.68,0:06:08.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.47,0:06:10.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会这么说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.03,0:06:12.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「真是蠢货」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.41,0:06:14.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「放弃算了」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.74,0:06:16.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「只会让你变得软弱」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.75,0:06:18.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「这根本不和你相称啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.66,0:06:20.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我真火大了  放弃吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.12,0:06:22.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  一定会这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.37,0:06:24.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,播磨拳儿！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.17,0:06:27.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么要做这种事啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.85,0:06:29.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我喜欢她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.40,0:06:32.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是喜欢得  喜欢得停不下来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.15,0:06:35.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,足够了  现在这样就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.79,0:06:37.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会继续狂奔下去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.93,0:06:39.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么？播磨同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.61,0:06:40.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.96,0:06:42.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓稳了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.26,0:06:49.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  正是这样  所以现在就开始喝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.41,0:06:53.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  反正这样倒头就睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.51,0:06:55.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就先喝着等你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.23,0:07:08.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦子  不好意思借摩托车一用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.06,0:07:10.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别问我理由
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.33,0:07:13.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个拳儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.59,0:07:16.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类还真是容易改变啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.76,0:07:21.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.00,0:07:33.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去  别磨磨蹭蹭的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.91,0:07:35.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机票的话大小姐应该已经用邮件传你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.81,0:07:36.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.98,0:07:39.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,播磨同学  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.37,0:07:40.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.11,0:07:48.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4楼  国际航班安检处
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.60,0:07:51.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GAL408次航班  G安检处
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.30,0:07:56.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  要在这中间找吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.22,0:08:01.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,G…G…G…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.77,0:08:05.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问GAL408次航班  飞往纽约是这里候机吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.31,0:08:07.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是想办理登机手续吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.05,0:08:09.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  护照？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.49,0:08:17.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.99,0:08:18.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位客人…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.93,0:08:26.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情就是这样  一定会争取赶在下一趟航班起飞前的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.46,0:08:28.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这段时间内  胡子你想办法做些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.66,0:08:30.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.17,0:08:38.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叶子小姐正带着护照和行李
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.37,0:08:41.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有当前的生活必需品来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.42,0:08:42.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叶子小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.40,0:08:44.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是笹仓老师
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.66,0:08:45.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖啡给你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.94,0:08:49.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是弦子…刑部老师的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.87,0:08:50.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老交情了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.05,0:08:55.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊  你和刑部老师住在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.29,0:08:57.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉有点不可思议呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.59,0:08:59.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.19,0:09:02.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我看来  她就像是大姐一般的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.57,0:09:03.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全没有什么别扭不别扭的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.75,0:09:06.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不会喜欢她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.51,0:09:07.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.62,0:09:10.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇到大姐后  绝对会对比自己年长的人失去兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.86,0:09:15.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是连那么漂亮又身材好的人都习惯了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.90,0:09:17.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对普通人可就更没兴趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.61,0:09:20.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过要是爱理或是我家八云的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.17,0:09:22.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般而言  的确如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.53,0:09:27.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我有我的美学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.66,0:09:29.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反而像大小姐那样的不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.49,0:09:30.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.53,0:09:31.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.70,0:09:32.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是很可爱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.21,0:09:35.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明啥都不懂  还摆出副很嚣张的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.03,0:09:36.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.35,0:09:39.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你喜欢哪种类型的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.44,0:09:42.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.97,0:09:46.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如有些呆的  有点迟钝的  无忧无虑的  没什么心机的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.89,0:09:49.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会大声说话的女孩…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.65,0:09:52.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  喜欢那种女孩啊  你真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.72,0:09:55.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么看  这都是你的翻版吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.73,0:09:57.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快注意到啊  笨女人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.05,0:10:03.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  事到如今也不期待这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.94,0:10:05.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  播磨同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.75,0:10:06.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.02,0:10:11.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么会觉得我还是见乌丸同学一面比较好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.57,0:10:15.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么特别的  只是直觉而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.06,0:10:16.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直觉？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.00,0:10:20.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了  虽然不知道那家伙会说些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.00,0:10:21.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些都是谎话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.40,0:10:23.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最起码不是真心话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.52,0:10:25.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.61,0:10:26.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.37,0:10:31.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天会有个…会有个男人喜欢上你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.77,0:10:34.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话  他就太可悲了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.38,0:10:36.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.31,0:10:40.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这就是男人的固执
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.93,0:10:45.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙不把你从你所爱的乌丸这边抢过来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.23,0:10:47.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就一定会抱憾终身的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.03,0:10:55.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.43,0:10:58.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干嘛啊  突然这么温顺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.06,0:11:00.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.74,0:11:02.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  播磨同学你戴墨镜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.00,0:11:04.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是想在我面前隐藏真面目？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.90,0:11:07.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.09,0:11:10.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和播磨同学以前见过面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.30,0:11:12.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧  是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.72,0:11:13.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.68,0:11:16.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从没见过你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.21,0:11:18.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人  一定是那个时候的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.96,0:11:19.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.78,0:11:20.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦子来的电话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.95,0:11:23.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行李到了  好快
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.18,0:11:24.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.00,0:11:29.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是十分感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.43,0:11:30.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事  没事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.86,0:11:33.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们好歹也算是老师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.25,0:11:36.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔也要帮点忙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.99,0:11:40.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快点出发的话  就要来不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.47,0:11:41.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.77,0:11:43.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拳儿  快去送送人家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.98,0:11:45.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切  要你烦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.55,0:11:48.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GAL408次航班的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.15,0:11:51.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请到4楼的国际航线候机厅…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.20,0:11:52.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这边  快点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.93,0:11:53.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.34,0:11:59.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了  小满
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.49,0:12:02.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的告别了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.03,0:12:06.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能祝福你顺利启程并送你出发的我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.90,0:12:08.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经很幸福了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.00,0:12:12.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  和你在同一班真好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.25,0:12:17.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出国安检口  在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.83,0:12:20.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  塚本
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.97,0:12:25.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事  我很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.86,0:12:28.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能在这个班里真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.90,0:12:32.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.34,0:12:38.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会再见面的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.58,0:12:44.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3月25日  塚本飞去了美国
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.45,0:12:46.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就是春天了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.37,0:12:49.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是最适合她的季节
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.09,0:12:57.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听到播磨同学在摩托上自言自语说的话了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.45,0:13:05.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对  其实在更早以前我就有预感了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.97,0:13:07.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.94,0:13:11.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的心意  让我觉得很自豪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.94,0:13:17.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢了  播磨同学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.77,0:13:29.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐踏上旅途后已经过了一天
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.32,0:13:37.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  一人份果然很快就干完了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.05,0:13:40.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊织？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.55,0:13:47.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？姐姐？姐姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.74,0:13:49.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时不会回来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.58,0:13:51.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你寂寞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.24,0:13:55.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我们来为她加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.35,0:14:03.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人生活感觉如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.07,0:14:06.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  现在还没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.66,0:14:07.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.98,0:14:10.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们好好热闹一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.89,0:14:13.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.96,0:14:14.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.64,0:14:16.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.05,0:14:17.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.68,0:14:20.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来晚了  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.80,0:14:21.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.07,0:14:26.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是步行祭的完结宴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.60,0:14:27.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多吃点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.03,0:14:29.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.38,0:14:31.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  我拿走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.19,0:14:40.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  播磨学长…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.01,0:14:45.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.75,0:14:59.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别把烟往人脸上喷  蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.54,0:15:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  振作点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.55,0:15:05.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你小子等等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.55,0:15:28.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.22,0:15:30.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.77,0:15:34.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  你受伤了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.46,0:15:41.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说别管我了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.44,0:15:44.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是倒在这里的你不对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.71,0:15:47.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  只是被女人甩了就去找人打架
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.72,0:15:49.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不敢相信  你还算男人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.24,0:15:52.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想玩纯情到什么程度
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.39,0:15:54.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是啰嗦死了  八婆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.03,0:15:57.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  对你来说也许是微不足道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.30,0:16:00.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最不爽你这点了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.14,0:16:06.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一辈子都不想和你这种成天换男人的女人有瓜葛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.32,0:16:07.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一看到我就反胃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.53,0:16:08.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.78,0:16:10.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太随便了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.66,0:16:13.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自以为是的一会说喜欢  一会说看不上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.64,0:16:15.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁会喜欢上这种女人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.48,0:16:20.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种随便的女人一定也很轻浮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.87,0:16:22.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许是这样…呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.35,0:16:23.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.30,0:16:25.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛啊  你这…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.38,0:16:31.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你哭个什么劲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.94,0:16:34.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没哭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.64,0:16:35.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少骗人了  刚刚…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.03,0:16:36.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没哭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.46,0:16:39.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.30,0:16:39.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.03,0:16:42.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,气死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.75,0:16:44.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什么资格这么说我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.33,0:16:46.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.92,0:16:47.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少自以为是了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.95,0:16:49.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是一样的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.93,0:16:51.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交往一次就够了  你明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.19,0:16:54.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到一个喜欢的男生就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.75,0:16:56.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那实在太难了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.97,0:16:59.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长得可爱也有可爱的烦恼啊
